high_descs: Turn around, move to the island.
Pick up the potato on the island.
Turn left, bring the potato to the microwave on the counter to your left.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the heated potato the fridge behind, on the other side of the island.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around to face the countertop.
Pick up the potato farthest to the right on the countertop.
Turn around to walk to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave, removing it again.
Turn around and walk around the counter to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato in the microwave to put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go to the counter on the right of the stove.
Grab the potato that is between you and the green sponge.
Turn around and go to the microwave that is on the opposite counter.
Cook the potato in the microwave and take it back out.
Turn around and take the potato to the fridge on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the potato into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato into a fridge.
